## 8. [QuizResult](file:///c:/Users/francis/OneDrive/Desktop/DJANGO%20PROJECT/e-learning/courses/models.py#147-158)
```python
class QuizResult(models.Model):
    user = models.ForeignKey(User, ...)
    quiz = models.ForeignKey(Quiz, ..., related_name='results')
```
| Pros | Cons / Problems |
| :--- | :--- |
| ✅ Tracks every attempt with score and pass/fail | ✅ `related_name='results'` makes queries clean |
| ✅ Has `is_passed` for quick filtering | ✅ No major issues |

